      <p class="base--p">In this demo, you're engaging with a banking virtual assistant. The assistant simulates a few
        scenarios, such as making a credit card payment, booking an appointment with a banker and choosing a credit
        card. Watson can understand your entries and respond accordingly.
        <br><br><strong>Hint: </strong>You can navigate the tasks by saying <strong>go back</strong>, or <strong>start over</strong>.
        You can also move
        between scenarios by using the navigation buttons.</p>
      <iframe style="width:100%; height:659px; border: solid 1px #909090; padding: 1px;" src="https://watson-conversation-duo-dev.ng.bluemix.net/"></iframe>
      <p>This demo is trained on a specific set of banking tasks which do not use actual banking data. Click on the
        "See all features" button in the top left-hand corner of the demo to start a scenario.
      </p>
      <h2 class="base--h2">Ready to get started?</h2>
